Package org.apache.commons.mail.resolver

Contains implementation classes to resolve data sources from the following locations:
  • class path
  • file system
  • URL
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataSourceBaseResolver
    Base class for various resolvers.
    DataSourceClassPathResolver
    Creates a DataSource based on an class path.
    DataSourceCompositeResolver
    A composite data source resolver.
    DataSourceFileResolver
    Creates a DataSource based on an URL.
    DataSourceUrlResolver
    Creates a DataSource based on an URL.
